title: Spot Bitcoin ETFs reach $37B in AUM, roughly one-third of gold ETF assets
description:
US-based spot Bitcoin ETFs have accumulated close to $37 billion in assets under management (AUM) within the first 25 days of trading, according to market data. Incidentally, the total AUM of Bitcoin ETFs is a sizeable fraction of the overall AUM of gold ETFs, according to data shared by Bitcoin Archive. The $37 billion AUM […]
